display_long_description:
"im gonna throw up" is a game in which you play as a legless ape, collecting bananas in waves with special power-ups you can get from berries that aid you in your victory. Do you have what it takes to throw up?

[media]

Compete with friends in a private game or find an already existing group to play with in this chaotic game. Play in an abandoned facility, an ancient temple of once great apes that don't quite appreciate your presence, or maybe have some fun at an arcade where pixels come to life (literally)!

[media]

- Quick game matchmaking, private game availability
- Multiple maps to play in
- Customizable player
